items: Marciano, a noble Siennois, his General.
Borasco, Captain of the rebels guard.
Cassio, Leonardo, two noble Gentlemen of quality.
Pantaloni, Becabunga, two rich gulls, in favour with the Ladies.
Manduco, an arrogant Pedant, challenging power over Becabunga.
A Servant, Partuysans, Drums, Trumpets, Souldiers, &c.
Arabella, A Siennois Lady, beloved of Marciano.
Chrysolina, Marionerta, two Ladies of honour.
